{"tid":1825133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拒交代毒氣 屯門區會反對警加薪","createTime":"2020-01-15T04:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T04:37:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"090b19454a41dcf1474f9f8e584c17b6e6a45db3","tid":1825133,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200115/TCXO2CZ6SPKKBF3HR6SBY66BHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200115%2FTCXO2CZ6SPKKBF3HR6SBY66BHA%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBpE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=8fedb6b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200115%2FTCXO2CZ6SPKKBF3HR6SBY66BHA%2F&h=4b45d1dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200115/TCXO2CZ6SPKKBF3HR6SBY66BHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n拒交代毒氣 屯門區會反對警加薪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200115/large/1579020179_7606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200115%2Flarge%2F1579020179_7606.jpg&h=55a21ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王德源<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】屯門區區議會昨召開特別會議，討論去年10月28日發生毒氣事件和警暴問題，但警方拒絕派員出席會議，議員不滿警方不作為，無視區內違法事件，只集中花時間精力打擊示威者：「警察乜嘢都唔做又要加人工！」有議員建議屯門區議會去信立法會財務委員會，表達屯門區議會反對警察加薪的立場。<br />\n<br />\n議員斥警與民作對<br />\n<br />\n區議會昨討論「10.28毒氣事件及相關警暴問題」，不過警方卻沒有派員列席。屯門社區網絡議員潘智鍵發言時，10月28日屯門發生疑似催淚煙事件，導致很多人不適，當時有居民更到警方位於屯門大興行動基地，要求警方交代是否在測試催淚煙，但最後遭警方竟以催淚彈還擊，故議員要求警方出席會議回應事件，是要為受害人討回公道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200115/large/1579020178_5754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200115%2Flarge%2F1579020178_5754.jpg&h=37285386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王德源力斥警方以「刺激性氣體」字眼，來取代屯門大興基地洩漏「毒氣事件」。<br />\n<br />\n屯門社區網絡議員王德源則留意到，警方書面回應竟以「刺激性氣體」來取代區議會議程字眼所指的「毒氣事件」、「警暴」，對警暴隻字不提。另一民主派議員羅佩麗指，警方現時是站在市民對面，與市民作對：「我真係唔知點解要加人工畀佢哋，佢哋𠵱家係不作為，然後又要加人工，佢哋又唔巡邏，無視違法事件，仲話加人工，係不合理要求。」 民主黨議員何杏梅則建議屯門區議會向立法會財務委員會發信，表達反對政府向警方加薪的撥款申請。<br />\n<br />\n警方在書面回應中指，就10.28屯門有刺激性氣體發現報告，警方當日已澄清，當日日間並沒有在屯門使用過催淚氣體或其他任何不明氣體，警方沒有進一步補充。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姚國雄"},{"pid":"a764acab450221faccdf0d87c217ca00a4212d42","tid":1825133,"uid":304321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ew5n82d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEw5n82d.jpg&h=f6492f6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ae0ca0444fea1691b75c7952b5670e25a7f5ac1","tid":1825133,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"自己個牌都係寫不明氣體。。。。又屌人改字眼"},{"pid":"c49af7779babb532472f7b65d9a339f7e33eb889","tid":1825133,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"你漏tg就搵人出黎受靶<br />\n如果唔係你黑警既責任，咁大規模釋放有害氣體<br />\n咁你有無循刑事方法查啊屌你老母<br />\n無補充？屌你老母啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0040f85979ebfbec8d4fd7216c1f4be37296ec8b","tid":1825133,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:21:45.000Z","msg":"【第廿貳期牆紙】 為良知發聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1824896/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1824896/page/1</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBpE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=30995277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBpE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=f4eb5108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://n